{"data":[{"id":561831011,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c003e41ea3ef1b3bfedb62ce3a006084","url_token":"chan-chingky","name":"Amadeus Chan","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-60884fbd81fdc581913d3f5b16e17d91_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-60884fbd81fdc581913d3f5b16e17d91_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c003e41ea3ef1b3bfedb62ce3a006084","user_type":"people","headline":"CS Tsinghua","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":40,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561831011","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546005654,"updated_time":1546276268,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e还是先上清华北大吧，这样容易一些（大雾）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（update）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看了所谓的证明过程，逻辑上漏洞百出，看得真难受，虽然知道基本不可能是真的证明，还是有些失望...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e简要叙述一下作者的逻辑吧：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最简单的一个逻辑漏洞在于，作者propose了一个\"\\forall x, (B or C)\"这么一个statement，然后c是恒为真的，然后用很诡异的方法（也是漏洞百出的方法）证明了这个statement是真的... 拜托，既然c是恒为真的，那么这个statement必定是真的好么... 然后作者画风一转，诡异地证明出了C不是恒真的.... wtf????? （为啥会出这个结果，因为作者里面自创了一个很模糊的概念，然后在这里混淆了...）然后作者就说既然c是假的，那么上面的statement可以简化为\"\\forall x, B\"，然后他按照这个思路证明了若干个命题B1, B2, B3是正确的，然后因为哥德巴赫猜想等价于B1 and B2 and B3是正确的，然后就说证明完成了... \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然，猜想等价于B1 and B2 and B3这点是没问题的，但是证明B1，B2, B3是真的的过程只能说是bullshit，错漏百出，真的看不出是一个具有扎实数学基础的高中生写出来的东西...\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"还是先上清华北大吧，这样容易一些（大雾）（update）看了所谓的证明过程，逻辑上漏洞百出，看得